      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Another way is to use a field of an object. E.g. MyObj result = new MyObj();  ...; result.timeZone = ...;  ....;  return result.timezone; Note though, that as explained above, this exposes you to thread-safety problems. See <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/50341404/7092558\">stackoverflow.com/a/50341404/7092558</a>"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 108728,
      "reputation" : 33016,
