  "title" : "Variable used in lambda expression should be final or effectively final",
  "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>Variable used in lambda expression should be final or effectively final</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>When I try to use <code>calTz</code> it is showing this error.</p>\n\n<pre><code>private TimeZone extractCalendarTimeZoneComponent(Calendar cal, TimeZone calTz) {\n    try {\n        cal.getComponents().getComponents(\"VTIMEZONE\").forEach(component -&gt; {\n            VTimeZone v = (VTimeZone) component;\n            v.getTimeZoneId();\n            if (calTz == null) {\n                calTz = TimeZone.getTimeZone(v.getTimeZoneId().getValue());\n            }\n        });\n    } catch (Exception e) {\n        log.warn(\"Unable to determine ical timezone\", e);\n    }\n    return null;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
